<h2>Spanish Idioms in Practice (Monographie)</h2>
<h3>Understanding Language and Culture</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='2129'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
